Author: ZeenyxThePhoenix
Text: I keep saying this but you are way more likely to pass out if you're dehydrated. It's something I have to be constantly aware of nowadays. Without drinking constantly, my blood pressure can be 80/50 and then I'll get up and find myself on the floor minutes later.

Author: socioanxiety
Text: I'm glad your friend was there with you though.  It could have been much worse if she hadn't caught you. Hope you are feeling better!
